# proptest regression archive (M04 Phase 5).
#
# Source-doc anchor:
# `.planning/trajectory/04-deterministic-replay.md`, Phase 5.
#
# When a property check in `crates/chio-kernel/tests/replay_proptest.rs`
# fails, proptest writes the shrunk seed to `replay_proptest.txt` in this
# directory. Future runs replay that seed first so regressions stay caught
# even after the underlying RNG state changes.
#
# This directory must remain checked in even when empty so proptest's
# `FileFailurePersistence::Direct` target path is creatable on clean
# checkouts. The `.gitkeep` is a placeholder; do not delete it.
